'''Wikipidiya''' si yekh proyekto te kerdivel enchiklopedie ande sa e ćhibya la lumiyake. O proyekto shirden andi ćhon Yanuara le 2001 bershenske la englizikani wikipediyasa. Shai te avel yekh wikipedia pi fiteshsavi ćhib. Akana si la mai but sar 100 enchiklopedie pe verver ćhibya ([[List_of_Wikipedias|kathe]] shai te dikhes len). Shai te drabares o lako puranipen [[Wikipedia timeline|kathe]].

I Wikipediya labyarel [[Test-wp/rmy/Mesto software|mesto software]] (Richard Stallman godisardya kado konchepto).

Varekon shai te drabarel vai te lekhel janglimata kathe thai kana mangel te thol len le avre thaneste, trebul te liparel ke le janglimata avel la Wikipediyatar.

